00073 //! Calcule la viscosite dynamique de mélange (depend des fraction massique)<br>Voir Wilke  https://aip.scitation.org/doi/pdf/10.1063/1.1747673
00074 void Loi_Etat_Binaire_GP_base::calculer_mu_wilke()
00075 {
00076   const DoubleTab& tab_Y1 = le_fluide->inco_chaleur().valeurs();
00077   DoubleTab& tab_mu = le_fluide->viscosite_dynamique().valeurs();
00078 
00079   int i, n=tab_mu.size();
00080   for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++)
00081     {
00082       double m1om2 = massmol1_/massmol2_;
00083       double m2om1 = 1./m1om2;
00084       double mu1omu2 = mu1_/mu2_;
00085       double mu2omu1 = 1./mu1omu2;
00086 
00087 // XXX : Which is better ?
00088       double a1 = 1. + sqrt(mu1omu2) * pow(mu2omu1,0.25);
00089       double a2 = 1. + sqrt(mu2omu1) * pow(mu1omu2,0.25);
00090 // double a1 = 1. + sqrt(mu1omu2) * exp(0.25*log(mu2omu1));
00091 // double a2 = 1. + sqrt(mu2omu1) * exp(0.25*log(mu1omu2));
00092       double b1 = sqrt(8.*(1.+m1om2));
00093       double b2 = sqrt(8.*(1.+m2om1));
00094       double phi_12 = m1om2*a1*a1/b1;
00095       double phi_21 = m2om1*a2*a2/b2;
00096 
00097       double y1 = tab_Y1(i,0);
00098       double y2 = 1. - y1; //!< All about binary mixture !
00099 
00100       tab_mu(i,0) = (mu1_*y1)/(y1+y2*phi_12) + (mu2_*y2)/(y2+y1*phi_21);
00101     }
00102   tab_mu.echange_espace_virtuel();
00103   Debog::verifier("calculer_mu_wilke",tab_mu);
00104 }

00119 //! Calcule la viscosite dynamique
00120 void Loi_Etat_Binaire_GP_base::calculer_mu()
00121 {
00122   Champ_Don& mu = le_fluide->viscosite_dynamique();
00123   if (!sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,mu.valeur()))
00124     {
00125       if (sub_type(Champ_Fonc_Tabule,mu.valeur()))
00126         {
00127           Cerr << "We should not have a dynamic viscosity of type Champ_Fonc_Tabule !" << finl;
00128           Process::exit();
00129         }
00130       else
00131         calculer_mu_wilke();
00132     }
00133   else
00134     {
00135       Cerr << "We should not have a dynamic viscosity of type Champ_Uniforme !" << finl;
00136       Process::exit();
00137     }
00138 }

00158 //! Calcule la viscosite dynamique sur Schmidt
00159 void Loi_Etat_Binaire_GP_base::calculer_mu_sur_Sc()
00160 {
00161   /*
00162    * ====================================================================
00163    * Schmidt number : Sc = nu / D = mu / ( rho * D )
00164    * => rho * D = mu/Sc
00165    * species equation : div ( rho * D * grad Y1) = div ( mu/Sc * grad Y1)
00166    * ====================================================================
00167    */
00168 
00169   Champ_Don& mu_sur_Sc = le_fluide->mu_sur_Schmidt();
00170   const Champ_base& rho = le_fluide->masse_volumique();
00171   DoubleTab& tab_mu_sur_Sc = mu_sur_Sc.valeurs();
00172   const DoubleTab& tab_rho = rho.valeurs();
00173   const int n=tab_mu_sur_Sc.size();
00174 
00175   if (!sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,mu_sur_Sc.valeur()))
00176     {
00177       if (sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,rho))
00178         {
00179           Cerr << "We should not have a density field of type Champ_Uniforme !" << finl;
00180           Process::exit();
00181         }
00182       else
00183         for (int i=0 ; i<n ; i++) tab_mu_sur_Sc(i,0) = tab_rho(i,0)*diff_coeff_;
00184     }
00185   else
00186     {
00187       Cerr << "We should not have a mu_sur_Sc of type Champ_Uniforme !" << finl;
00188       Process::exit();
00189     }
00190 
00191   double temps_champ = rho.temps();
00192   mu_sur_Sc.valeur().changer_temps(temps_champ);
00193   tab_mu_sur_Sc.echange_espace_virtuel();
00194 }

00210 void Loi_Etat_Binaire_GP_base::calculer_nu_sur_Sc()
00211 {
00212   /*
00213    * ====================================================================
00214    * Schmidt number : Sc = nu / D
00215    * => D = nu/Sc
00216    * ====================================================================
00217    */
00218 
00219   Champ_Don& nu_sur_Sc = le_fluide->nu_sur_Schmidt();
00220   DoubleTab& tab_nu_sur_Sc = nu_sur_Sc.valeurs();
00221   const int n=tab_nu_sur_Sc.size();
00222 
00223   for (int i=0 ; i<n ; i++) tab_nu_sur_Sc(i,0) = diff_coeff_;
00224 
00225   double temps_champ = le_fluide->masse_volumique().temps();
00226   nu_sur_Sc.valeur().changer_temps(temps_champ);
00227   tab_nu_sur_Sc.echange_espace_virtuel();

00299 double Loi_Etat_Binaire_GP_base::calculer_masse_volumique(double P, double Y1) const
00300 {
00301   /*
00302    * Mixing species state equation
00303    * ===========================================================================
00304    * rho = ( P * M_mix ) / ( R * T)
00305    * with M_mix = 1 / (Y1/M1 + Y2/M2) = = M2 / (M2Y1/M1 + Y2)
00306    * But Y2 = 1 - Y1 => M_mix = M2 / (M2Y1/M1 + 1 -Y1) = M2 / (1 + Y1(M2/M1 -1))
00307    * ===========================================================================
00308    * See https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijheatmasstransfer.2020.120470
00309   */
00310   const double PM2 = P*massmol2_;
00311   const double RT = R_GAS*tempr_;
00312   const double mix = 1.0+Y1*(massmol2_/massmol1_-1.0);
00313   const double rh = PM2/(RT*mix);
00314 
00315   return rh;
00316 }
